# Product page features
Before every scenario the first step is to open browser (Chromium 88.0.4314.0) and go to 'SAMSUNG T220 Galaxy Tab A7 Lite 8.7" 32GB WiFi ezüst' product page
The user is not log in to ipon.hu

## 1_Product's color changing
* Change product's color
* The page goes to the silver coloured product

## 2_Sliding product picture
* Click on the product's picture
* Scroll to right the picture
* Showed second picture

## 3_Product save to the wishlist
* Click on 'Elmentem' button
* 'Bejelentkezés' pop-up comes up

## 4_'Értékelés' button work
* Click on 'értékelés' button
* Page scroll down to 'Vélemények' section

## 5_Show all product's specification
* Click on the 'Teljes specifikáció' button on the 'Specifikáció' section
* Showed all specification

## 6_Close all product's specification (BUG)
